room_title: Escape room "Jailbreak" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: So fun!  We did the Jailbreak room with our 18 and 20-year-old kids and friends. So challenging and fun trying to figure out the clues. Staff was very friendly and helpful. Great time, we got out with 2 minutes to go. Great setup, staff will help with hints if you are stuck, a fun time. Would definitely go back to try another one.
